🔢 Counter App

A simple web-based counter application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This app allows users to increment, decrement, and reset a counter with the click of a button.

🚀 Features

- Increment the counter
- Decrement the counter
- Reset the counter to zero
- Responsive design
- Clean and minimal UI

👨‍💻 How It Works

1. Open the app in your browser.
2. Click on the **"+"**, **"-"**, or **"Reset"** button.
3. The counter value will update in real time.

🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

